PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of Donald W. Wilson, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of James William McLellan, whose term has expired.
